snippet.title: Friendly Software - Microsoft Golf 1998 Edition - 1998
snippet.description:
For those who wants to rememorate this golf game that was SimGolf (also known as Sim Golf) developed by Friendly Software, but published by Microsoft Corporation in 1998.
